context:
KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;일리 있는 지적이군.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;You make a fair assessment.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그렇다면 이렇게 하도록 할까?&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;How about this, then?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;피할 수 없다면 신속하게 보여줄 테니 끝이 나면 곧바로 나를 만나러 오게나.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;If you are to see them anyway, allow me to save you the trouble and give you a quick run-down instead. Come visit me as soon as you finish watching my tale.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;이 이야기는 그자가 내 연구실 문을 들어오면서부터 시작이 되었네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;This tale began when that man walked into my laboratory.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그래, 나는 개인 연구실이 있었지. 엘리트 연구원을 위한 몇 안 되는 특권 중 하나였어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Yes, I had a personal laboratory all to myself. One of the few perks of being an elite researcher.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;가만 보자, 이 자가 어떻게 생겼더라.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Let me think… I don’t quite remember what he looked like.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;이런 느낌으로 생겼던 것 같기도 하네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Something like this, perhaps?&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;아무렴 어떤가. 그냥 원래대로 검열통제를 시키는 게 낫겠군.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Ah, whichever is the case—I was planning to censor his appearance anyway.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;당연하지만, 그건 가능성 같은 거창한 이유가 아니었네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Ah, but it had nothing to do with something so grandiose like his ‘potentiality’.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;날개는 고작 그런 이유로 뒷골목 출신을 채용하지 않지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;A Wing does not hire people from the Backstreets for something so insignificant.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;대외적으로 알려진 적은 없었지만, 로보토미 코퍼레이션 같은 경우는 트라우마였네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;While this information has never been publicly available, Lobotomy Corporation's primary criterion was ‘trauma’.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;끔찍하고, 극복하기 어려운 트라우마를 지닌 자일수록 우선순위가 높았네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Candidates with horrible, insurmountable trauma were often favored by the company.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그러다 보니 자연스럽게 뒷골목의 비율이 늘어났던 것뿐이었지.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;And, in an indirect way, it was only natural that they would begin to favor candidates who originate from the Backstreets.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;지금 봐도 정말 사람 말을 잘 듣지 않는 직원이었군.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Hm. What an unrelentingly stubborn employee he was, even in hindsight.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;그래, 인정하지. 그때 당시의 나는 조금 무료했던 것 같네.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;I will admit, I suppose I was overcome by a certain ennui back then.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;돌이켜 생각해 보면, 그런 쓸데없는 대화를 나누는 편이 그렇게 좋은 선택은 아니었어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;And in hindsight, it was foolish of me to engage in such inane conversations.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;아, 내 과거의 산물들이 공격해 오기 시작하는군.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Ah, the remnants of my past come to haunt us.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;어쩌면 저들이 정말 해를 끼치고 싶은 건 나일 수도 있을 걸세.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#ffffa1&gt;Perhaps it is I whom they truly wish to hurt.&lt;/color&gt;
